        "created_at": "2024-10-21T07:26:32.250Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Our project finally decided to use fdb as metadata storage. When verifying the backup and recovery, we found that the data recovery was very slow.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/foundationdb/original/2X/c/c108adffe9247f4ca1b69d75408b068fd686d3c8.png\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/rxEKn4FSEBO8J4tju3HjjcTug1a.png?dl=1\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/foundationdb/optimized/2X/c/c108adffe9247f4ca1b69d75408b068fd686d3c8_2_690x125.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"rxEKn4FSEBO8J4tju3HjjcTug1a\" width=\"690\" height=\"125\" srcset=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/foundationdb/optimized/2X/c/c108adffe9247f4ca1b69d75408b068fd686d3c8_2_690x125.png, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/foundationdb/optimized/2X/c/c108adffe9247f4ca1b69d75408b068fd686d3c8_2_1035x187.png 1.5x, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/foundationdb/optimized/2X/c/c108adffe9247f4ca1b69d75408b068fd686d3c8_2_1380x250.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"282828\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">3486\u00d7634 234 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>The recovery task lasted about 10 minutes.<br>\nrestore cluster</p>\n<p>fdb&gt; status</p>\n<p>Using cluster file `/etc/foundationdb/fdb.cluster\u2019.</p>\n<p>Configuration:<br>\nRedundancy mode        - triple<br>\nStorage engine         - memory-2<br>\nEncryption at-rest     - disabled<br>\nCoordinators           - 3<br>\nUsable Regions         - 1</p>\n<p>Cluster:<br>\nFoundationDB processes - 6<br>\nZones                  - 5<br>\nMachines               - 5<br>\nMemory availability    - 7.2 GB per process on machine with least available<br>\nRetransmissions rate   - 1 Hz<br>\nFault Tolerance        - 1 machines<br>\nServer time            - 10/21/24 15:10:46</p>",
